HEADWORD: Prologue
<hw>Pro"logue</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F., fr. L.
<ets>prologus</ets>, fr. Gr. <?/, fr. <?/ to say beforehand; <?/ before
+ <?/ to say. See <er>Logic</er>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
